Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: django-teamwork
Version: 0.2.0
Summary: Django app that offers an authorization backend with support for per-object permissions based on combinations of Teams, Roles, and Policies.
Home-page: http://github.com/lmorchard/django-teamwork
Author: Les Orchard
Author-email: me@lmorchard.com
License: BSD
Description: django-teamwork is a Django app that offers an authorization backend with
        support for per-object permissions based on combinations of Teams, Roles, and
        Policies.
        
